    <div class="main review-item" id="2954960">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2954960/" class="title-link">一本好书怎么翻译成这个样子？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2954960"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4482921/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4482921/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">luwg001</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-01-25"
      class="main-meta">2010-01-25 15:47:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2954960_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  因为研究在书店买了这本书，越读越生气，一本好书怎么翻译成这个样子？  就像是一个刚学习外语的大学生翻的，晦涩不说，动不动简单直译，一句话被切成几段，让人丧失阅读的乐趣。  好歹“商务出版社”出的，也是个知名“老店”，真令人怀疑其组织编辑能力。   

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2954960/#comments">(6回应)</a>
