      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4876302/" class="title-link">給2星純粹是因為翻譯～～</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4876302"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/reiayanamijack/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3949585-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/reiayanamijack/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">蒹葭</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-03-25"
      class="main-meta">2011-03-25 14:57:02</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4876302_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  這個譯本還是我大學時候讀的，毫無印象。讀了一點colin smith的英譯本後，才發現這個中文版翻譯問題的嚴重。2星有一星是因為梅洛龐蒂的名字，另外一星是因為無法打零星。  英譯本五星，毫無疑問。

