        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33397964/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33397964/" class="">第28页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/80853821/" class=" " title="拖鞋帮">拖鞋帮</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="33397964">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">当认知恒长性遭到破坏，现象与刺激不一致，比如同长两条直线，加上背景相反的箭头，就不再长度一直的视觉感，这个问题确实让我感到好奇。因为分开两个解释，都说得通，可是放在一起，是第一次学习。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-11-13 07:49</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
